\begin_layout Standard
It is in our self-interest to be good.
 I will argue this thesis through two parts.
 First, being good reaps more long term rewards.
 Second, being good benefits more as a whole, rather than individually.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The main arguments are drawn from two texts: the philosophy textbook,  
\emph on
The Fundamentals of Ethics
